1.title: Episode VI: Revenge of the Fanboy
1.plot: George Lucas has announced his retirement, much to the dismay of Ralphie, who, like Darth Maul at the end of Episode I, is quite beside himself.

imdb.plot outline: 'Skippy's Basement' is a Fandom-oriented show that will offer news, commentaries, sketches, and guest interviews. The show is hosted by Thaddeus J. 'Skippy' Kozlowskowiecz, and Ralphie 'The Wrench' Robbaccio, a couple of life-long, nerdy, fanboy types from Brooklyn, NY. Produced for Geektastic Nebula by TurboMandala Entertainment, and Skippy's Mother, Mrs. Kozlowskowiecz (Hey, it's her house, her rules...).
